==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Term insurance
<hw>Term insurance</hw>. <def>Insurance for a specified term providing
for no payment to the insured except upon losses during the term, and
becoming void upon its expiration.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Terminus</ent>⟦br⟧
